Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家起来了 到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是新手潜水员的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的名字是大濑崎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是清早却有很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为周末不只是关东
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国各地的潜水员都会聚集而来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都会从这里诞生数名潜水员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到这个时候了啊 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 海洋实习我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let´s go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火鸟老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占到好位子了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我是喜欢才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想和努力的学生们一起尽兴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你们几个 把行李放过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 轻松轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有气势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次的心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 有点儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在兴奋的成分更大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想去看自己未知的美妙事物 和闪光一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天潜水的是双子组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光小点组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一共五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先慢慢浮潜在水面游到那边的浮标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮标上系着通到海底的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点你好好抓住绳子慢慢下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 所有人带好装备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始潜伴间检查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么从我开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BCD 给气装置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BCD 给气装置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配重OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泻气系统OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气阀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残压
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调节器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到水齐腰深的地方就穿上脚蹼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水渐渐进入湿式潜水服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能确实感受到自己潜入大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷水很快就会习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 扶着我穿上脚蹼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 去浮标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳不已 心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在视野下方延伸开的蓝色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海底渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从水面射进来的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被无限深邃的湛蓝吸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗小点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 潜入大海之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要将至今为止学到的东西都实践一遍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸进去的光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深邃的苍蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀？ 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚蹼少了一只哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可找不到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 海洋实习就这样结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 从上面掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所不知道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 有很多泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气泡柱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那全都是下面的潜水员们的呼出的气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在下面等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这海面下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那深邃苍蓝的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有怎样的世界在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 心理准备OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到大海的世界里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚为止不安的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时变为了兴奋的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地 慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然最棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来海边就是该吃炒面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵在刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳压平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看不到水面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会突然分不清哪边是上面哪边是下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呼出的气泡慢慢向上浮起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉了我哪边是上方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在依旧深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然视野开阔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是雾气消散一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是海中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是从上面眺望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对看不到这景色的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要将至今为止学到的东西都实践一遍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小点不擅长的清除面镜进水开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油小点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不用调节器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清除面镜进水大师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 中性浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在水中保持既不上浮也不下沉的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过体内的空气调节浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调节器寻回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 手势信号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气体用尽了 请给我空气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面镜脱下 戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一眨眼的功夫一套就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像奶奶说得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起头看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你眼前 广大而有趣的世界正无限展开着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数升起的气泡柱全都是潜水员的呼气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是苍蓝世界为我展现的生命之证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会有这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在那一天放弃太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被心情所吞噬太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能说出自己的恐惧 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能来到这里真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噼里啪啦的声音 是什么声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气泡好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗地一下冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿像水母一样  一会儿像盘子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有鱼好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的黄色的还有在地面上走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和闪光一起开始的日志本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里开始写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是这种感觉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想写的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不写吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿式潜水服就会有这种独特的疲劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 回忆起今天的事就会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs53\bord0\shad0\pos(324,230)\frz-13\an4\1c&H0F0F0F&\b0}小茜\N双叶 还精神吗？\N──────────\N炎热的天气\N一直持续着啊\N有没有感到疲乏呢？\N茜\N-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 小茜发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是潜水部的海洋实习…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord0\shad0\pos(1350,600)\frz24\an4\1c&H0F0F0F&\b0}小茜\N好厉害～ ！\N──────────\N好厉害好厉害好厉害！\N初次潜入大海！\N恭喜你\N不过双叶\N很适合海里呢～\N茜\N-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 全体起立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在公布海洋实习的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大木双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向你授予开放水域潜水员的证明 「C卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那个只是样品 之后会给你送正品的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个噼里啪啦的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许是大海在为我祝贺的鼓掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个噼里啪啦的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是短脊鼓虾的声音或者是海浪拍到岩石上的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又说出声来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大海的鼓掌这个想法也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我们还在那里潜水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么闪光要道谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很长很顺很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始看到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在海里一样摇曳着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得像是人鱼一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又分到了一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就擅自决定一定要和这孩子搞好关系 一起潜入大海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常会擅自做决定自己一个人开心 停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有时也会因此给对方添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我觉得绝对会开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人也会不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不是这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  要说我想要说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我完全说不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事的 我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从闪光那里获得了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是大海中深蓝的世界 还是闪闪发光浮起的气泡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有可爱的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是闪光教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加入潜水部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因为闪光给我的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢 我发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光给予我的东西我全都非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢的东西增加了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经的我 没有说得上非常喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是害怕喜欢上什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以将自己变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也讨厌那样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想喜欢上更多更多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望闪光能教给我很多你非常喜欢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 要让你教给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅自这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 是为了那件事道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点喜欢上我喜欢的全部事物了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点现在喜欢上自己了呢
